# This CODEOWNERS file enforces review requirements for 
# changes to the Open Trust Registry state.

# Global default
*       @founding-maintainer-1 @founding-maintainer-2

# The actual registry entries
# Any addition, deletion, or key rotation requires at least 
# 1 approval from the core maintaining group PLUS 
# 1 approval from the independent review council.
/registry/issuers/*.json @review-council @founding-maintainers

# The revocation list
# Same high-bar requirement for revocations to prevent abuse
/registry/revocations.json @review-council @founding-maintainers

# The Manifest
# This file is generated via the signing ceremony. Modifying it directly 
# requires unanimous maintainer consent to coordinate the 3-of-5 threshold.
/registry/manifest.json @founding-maintainers
